sentences: Pegz has been a part of the Australian hip hop scene since 1992, and has released four full-length studio albums.
In 2000, he scored a job at Obese Records, a specialist hip-hop music store in Prahran.
He released his first recording, an EP, Pegasus, on the Obese label in 2001, followed by a studio album, Capricorn Cat in 2003 and Axis in 2005.
